net.cloud.server.file.request.handler

Class RequestHandler

  • java.lang.Object
    • net.cloud.server.file.request.handler.RequestHandler

  • public class RequestHandler
extends Object
    A class which serves as a facade to other, more specific, handlers. These handler classes are purposed with taking whatever action is needed to fulfill the request and get it ready for action to be taken upon it.
